user_photos` table seems to be used instead of `photo_urls` JSON array. This is 
actually better per db.md which shows a separate `user_photos` table in the ER d
iagram. But the migration name is misleading.\n\nKey issues I've found:\n1. **Ap
p.dart /home route**: Still uses placeholder `Scaffold(body: Center(child: Text(
